at a settlement with exxonmobil has proven difficult with venezuela offering book value for exxonmobils assets and exxonmobil asking for as much as  billion this and a number of other matters including the claims of conocophillips remain before the world bank’s international centre for settlement of investment disputes pdvsa has paid compensation for assets it has nationalized including  million paid to exxonmobil on february   in compensation for nationalization of exxonmobils venezuelan assets in  and  million to be paid beginning in  to us firms williams cos inc and exterran holdings inc for natural gas assets nationalized in  safetyedit there have been worsening safety problems since  culminating in a gas leak at the paraguaná refinery complex in august  which caused an explosion killing  people and damaging  homes another major fire broke out at the el palito refinery in september  presidents of pdvsaedit eulogio del pino september  – present exploration geophysics universidad central de venezuela rafael ramírez november  – september  minister of energy and oil  msc energy policy – ucv bsc mechanical engineering – ula alí rodríguez araque april  – october  minister of energy  secretary general opec  lic economics  ucv gastón parra luzardo february   april  academic vicerector – luz – dean of the school of social sciences – luz – lic economics  luz guaicaipuro lameda montero october  – february  brigadier general of the venezuelan army and electrical engineering university of the pacific msc economic planning  héctor ciavaldini august   october  roberto mandini february   august  luis giusti march  – february  msc petroleum engineering – tu bsc petroleum engineering  luz gustavo roosen march  – march  minister of education  ma comparative law – new york university nyu ba law – ucab andres sosa pietri march  – march  juan chacín guzmán october  – march  brigido r natera february  – october  bs geology universidad central de venezuela  mba stanford university  hum