fense of the nation’s energy sovereignty and to the duty of adding the greatest possible value to oil resources under the principles of unity teamwork spirit of collaboration and efficient use of reserves all of pdvsa’s units are focused on such concepts as the sovereign use of national energy resources and the promotion of technological independence the latter is being achieved through the development and strengthening of venezuelanmade technologies these efforts generate quality jobs economic growth and lead to the creation of wealth and welfare for the venezuelan people transparency and clear control of accounts is another fundamental value of pdvsa in accordance with this principle the performance of the board of directors executives and workers is generally evaluated taking into consideration their commitment to the honest and moderate administration of corporate resources citgo corporate citgo fueling good mystik lubes citgo corporate citgo fueling good mystik lubes citgo corporate citgo fueling good mystik lubes citgo corporate clarion lubricants consumers    business    news room    about citgo    careers    contact us    privacy policy    terms and conditions    site map concerns  complaints site    california supply chains disclosure    marketnet login   citgo petroleum corporation venezuelan national petroleum co  annual and transition report foreign private issuer f item  information on the company about edgar online  login dashboard todaycompany industry search screener analytics      enter your email for a free trial the following is an excerpt from a f sec filing filed by venezuelan national petroleum co on  next section previous section  use sections to navigate through the document  form f part i item  offer statistics and expected timetable item  key information item  information on the company item  operating and financial review and prospects results of operations compared to  item  directors senior management and employees name and title item  m